Home.About:
OONI Run is a web platform that you can use to generate mobile deep links and widget code to coordinate OONI Probe website testing.

Specifically, you can use OONI Run to create links or widget code for testing websites (of your choice) for censorship and coordinating website censorship testing with other OONI Probe users.
